<plot>Djamel and Paco are recovering from a sea accident in an Italian hospital. They are very different and their views of the world are completely opposite. As Paco is not able to move from his bed, Djamel describes to him all the beautiful things he sees outside: the sea, the beach, the fishermen... With a bit of time and talking they realize that they are not as different as they initially thought, until destiny knocks on the door...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?152791</url></doc>
